body.data:
SELECT 
  I.ID_INTERCORRENCIA,
  I.ID_FILIAL,
  I.NOME_MOTOBOY,
  I.COD_MOTOBOY,
  TO_CHAR(I.DATA_INTERCORRENCIA, 'DD/MM/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS DATA_INTERCORRENCIA,
  I.CIDADE,
  I.SAIDA_ID,
  I.NUMPED,
  P.CODUSUR AS CODRCA,
  u.NOME AS NOME_RCA,
  I.TEMPO_INTERCORRENCIA,
  I.DESCRICAO,
  I.NOME_LANCAMENTO,
  I.CODWINTHOR_LANCAMENTO,
  I.URLS_FOTOS,
  I.APROVACAO_INTERCORRENCIA,
  I.NOME_QUEM_APROVOU,
  I.CODE_WINTHOR_QUEM_APROVOU,
  I.JUSTIFICATIVA_APROVACAO,
  I.DATA_HORA_APROVACAO,
  I.ID_CATEGORIA_INTERCORRENCIA,
  I.CATEGORIA_INTERCORRENCIA,
  C.CODCLI AS CODIGO_CLIENTE,
  C.CLIENTE AS NOME_CLIENTE,
  F.CODIGO AS CODIGO_FILIAL,
  F.RAZAOSOCIAL AS RAZAOSOCIAL_FILIAL
FROM WINDOW.INTERCORRENCIA_PEDIDOS I,
     WINDOW.PCPEDC P,
     WINDOW.PCUSUARI U,
     WINDOW.PCCLIENT C,
     WINDOW.PCFILIAL F
WHERE I.NUMPED = P.NUMPED(+)
  AND P.CODUSUR = U.CODUSUR
  AND P.CODCLI = C.CODCLI
  AND P.CODFILIAL = F.CODIGO
  AND I.DATA_INTERCORRENCIA BETWEEN 
      TO_DATE('{{ moment(DatePicker_Data_Inicio.selectedDate).format("DD-MM-YYYY") }}', 'DD-MM-YYYY')
  AND TO_DATE('{{ moment(DatePicker_Data_Fim.selectedDate).format("DD-MM-YYYY") }}', 'DD-MM-YYYY') + 1 - INTERVAL '1' SECOND
ORDER BY I.DATA_INTERCORRENCIA DESC;
